                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen and nitrogen mixed storage device and application thereof in ammonia synthesis",
                    "一种氢气氮气混合储存装置及在氨合成中的应用"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen and nitrogen mixed storage device and application in ammonia synthesis, and relates to the field of gas storage, the hydrogen and nitrogen mixed storage device comprises a nitrogen inlet pipeline, a hydrogen inlet pipeline, a mixed storage tank and a discharging pipeline, the mixed storage tank is provided with a first gas inlet and a second gas inlet, the nitrogen inlet pipeline is communicated with the first gas inlet, and the hydrogen inlet pipeline is communicated with the second gas inlet; the nitrogen inlet pipeline is communicated with the first gas inlet, the hydrogen inlet pipeline is communicated with the second gas inlet, the nitrogen inlet pipeline and the hydrogen inlet pipeline are each provided with an adjusting ball valve, an electromagnetic flowmeter and a pressure sensor, the pressure sensor and a temperature sensor are arranged in the mixing storage tank, and the bottom end of the mixing storage tank is communicated with a one-way breather valve. Hydrogen can be stored more safely, stably, economically and efficiently, hydrogen and nitrogen are accurately mixed in proportion, impurity gas is prevented from being mixed, and the device is suitable for the field of renewable energy hydrogen production and synthesis ammonia."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种氢气氮气混合储存装置及在氨合成中的应用，涉及气体储存领域，包括氮气进气管道、氢气进气管道、混合储存罐和出料管道，所述混合储存罐设置有第一进气口和第二进气口，所述氮气进气管道与第一进气口相连通，所述氢气进气管道与第二进气口相连通，所述氮气进气管道和氢气进气管道上均设置有调节球阀、电磁流量计和压力传感器，所述混合储存罐的内部设置有压力传感器、温度传感器，所述混合储存罐的底端连通有单向呼吸阀。本发明能够更加安全稳定、经济高效的储存氢气，氢氮比例精确混合，避免杂质气体混入，适用可再生能源制氢合成氨领域。"
                }
            ]
